No. 80,

Misc.

Westover v. United States. Petitioner *925pro se.

*924C. A. 9th Cir. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari granted. The case is transferred to the appellate docket and set for oral argument immediately following No. 397, Misc.

*925Solicitor General Cox, Assistant Attorney General Vinson, Beatrice Rosenberg and Jerome M. Feit for the United States.
